                I will be billed the amount above on a monthly basis</label>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div style="text-align: center">
                <button class="k-button" id="editadproduct" type="button">
                    <span class="k-back k-icon"></span>EDIT</button>
                <button class="k-button" id="getLaunchAdProduct" type="submit" name="Command" value="LaunchAdProduct">
